Name:             R-CRAN-%{packname}
Version:          1.0.3
Release:          3%{?dist}%{?buildtag}
Summary:          Cluster Analysis via Nonparametric Density Estimation

License:          GPL-2
URL:              https://cran.r-project.org/package=%{packname}
Source0:          %{url}&version=%{packver}#/%{packname}_%{packver}.tar.gz


BuildRequires:    R-devel
Requires:         R-core
BuildRequires:    R-CRAN-geometry 
BuildRequires:    R-methods 
Requires:         R-CRAN-geometry 
Requires:         R-methods 

%description
Cluster analysis via nonparametric density estimation is performed.
Operationally, the kernel method is used throughout to estimate the
density. Diagnostics methods for evaluating the quality of the clustering
are available. The package includes also a routine to estimate the
probability density function obtained by the kernel method, given a set of
data with arbitrary dimensions.

